trans-unit.source: Converts an <xref:System.Collections.IList> collection of UShort number values to and from instances of <xref:System.String>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Collections.IList>인스턴스 <xref:System.String>안내 하십시오.</xref:System.String> UShort 숫자 값의 컬렉션</xref:System.Collections.IList> 으로 변환
